title: The Historical Jesus: Ancient Evidence for the Life of Christ -
description:
The Historical Jesus: Ancient Evidence for the Life of Christ - Gary R. Habermas  epub/mobi

Examining archaeological, textual and extra-biblical evidence, the author examines the evidence for the existence and deity of Jesus. 
"Who do you say that I am?" - Jesus
The Historical Jesus examines this mystery,and the age-old question of Christ's identity...

"The Historical Jesus is a careful, accessible analysis and critique of the various approaches to the historical Jesus. "  -Dr. J.P. Moreland, Professor of Philosophy, Biola University

"This is an up-to-date, timely, and scholarly treatment of a crucial dimension of the Christian faith by one of the foremost historical apologists in America today?" -Dr. Norm Geisler,
